messages.content: I need help with my order.
Sure, can you provide your order ID?
My package hasn't arrived yet.
I apologize for the delay. Can I have your tracking number?
Can you help me change my account email?
Of course, please provide your current email address.
I want to cancel my subscription.
I'm sorry to hear that. Can you tell us why you're cancelling?
I'm having issues with logging in.
Have you tried resetting your password?
Do you offer international shipping?
Yes, we do. Which country are you shipping to?
Can I update my payment method online?
Yes, you can update it in the billing section of your account.
Is there a way to track my support tickets?
Yes, you can view them in your account dashboard.
What are your business hours?
Our business hours are 9 AM to 5 PM, Monday through Friday.
How can I redeem my reward points?
You can redeem them at checkout on your next purchase.
